{"tid":867584,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"［激動］Crocodile Skink 勁似Toothless 真係好撚得意!!","createTime":"2018-10-18T19:42:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T05:28:09.000Z","uid":157827,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6411b35400ce1ddc09e38c9803d2063c03d8f311","tid":867584,"uid":157827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T19:42:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解世界上存在咁得意嘅生物<br />\n勁似夢工場隻Toothless<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n原諒我好激動 <br />\n因為佢真係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好撚得意又有霸氣</span> <br />\n<br />\n點解咁細粒可以咁似鱷魚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> [/size=5]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/19/033622_fa9540546fd7cbeaf0a82376049223a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F19%2F033622_fa9540546fd7cbeaf0a82376049223a4.png&h=debe9458&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/19/033628_5b6a6b515f7cf91f6f628376f0b3ca56.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F19%2F033628_5b6a6b515f7cf91f6f628376f0b3ca56.png&h=3ee988a3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/19/033634_507c4c01541d3ced1c2b0d2a29be1588.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F19%2F033634_507c4c01541d3ced1c2b0d2a29be1588.png&h=45858ae7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/19/033638_c3cfa60a6fec78b10725e61545298089.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F19%2F033638_c3cfa60a6fec78b10725e61545298089.png&h=f1b8c3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/19/033639_e5fe0a1